name: Running Fish Story
description: Running Fish Story. Once upon a time, a worker who was very poor found some work as a fisherman's helper.He was paid a few fish a day, and this kept him and his wife alive, though barely. One day the worker caught an especially pretty little fish. As he turned it over in his hands, he thought, "Why, what a marvelous fish this is!" Suddenly the fish spoke to him, in a human voice. "The Sea & The End Of Hope"
